{"word":"τυφλός","slug":"τυφλός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>τυφλός, ή, όν</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:τυφόω\">τυφόω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> in central sense of inability to see, <b>blind<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adj.\">adj.</a> <b><a href='B:500 9:1'>J 9:1</a>, <a href='B:500 9:18'>18</a>, <a href='B:500 9:24'>24</a>; <a href='B:510 13:11'>Ac 13:11</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as noun <b><a href='B:470 9:27'>Mt 9:27f</a>; <a href='B:480 8:22'>Mk 8:22f</a>; <a href='B:490 7:21'>Lk 7:21f</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> in imagery of lack of understanding in the cognitive sphere (a common motif in the ancient world), <b>blind<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adj.\">adj.</a> <b><a href='B:470 15:14'>Mt 15:14</a>; <a href='B:470 23:16'>23:16</a>, <a href='B:470 23:24'>24</a>, <a href='B:470 23:26'>26</a>; <a href='B:500 9:40'>J 9:40f</a>; <a href='B:680 1:9'>2 Pt 1:9</a>; <a href='B:730 3:17'>Rv 3:17</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as noun<b> <a href='B:470 23:17'>Mt 23:17</a>, <a href='B:470 23:19'>19</a>; <a href='B:520 2:19'>Ro 2:19</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Τύρος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:τυφλόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}